Source: pg-stl
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/nadyaloseva/pg_ts_analysis

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-stl
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-stl
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Time series analysis functions for PostgreSQL
  pg_stl provides time series analysis functions for PostgreSQL, including
  ACF, PACF, STL decomposition, and Holt-Winters forecasting.
